headline: THE RITZ® BRAND CONFIRMS A SALTY BIG GAME RETURN IN 2026
summary: RITZ®, America's favorite cracker,1 will return to the Big Game on Feb. 8, 2026, with a 30-second advertisement airing during the third quarter. This will mark the third consecutive year that a Mondelēz International snack brand will make an ad-break appearance—because sometimes great things really do come in threes.
